20:47.400 --> 20:49.986
<i>I was home with a stomach ache
because I snuck in the kitchen</i>

20:50.070 --> 20:51.905
<i>and ate a whole tub
of chocolate ice cream.</i>

20:51.988 --> 20:53.823
<i>I haven't eaten chocolate since.</i>

20:54.324 --> 20:56.785
<i>My Uncle Frank
raised me in Chicago.</i>

20:57.077 --> 21:00.872
<i>I went to Northwestern, where I
majored in Computer Science.</i>

21:01.915 --> 21:03.375
<i>I never married.</i>

21:03.875 --> 21:05.627
<i>I have no children.</i>

